# Secrets. .env is the classic dotenv convention; .envrc is direnv's.
# Both are mentioned in docs/pi-cassettes.md and the repo's key-hygiene
# guidance, so block them at the repo level rather than relying on a
# user-level global gitignore.
.env
.envrc

# Generated files (build-time precompilation)
packages/runtime/generated/

