# Defense-in-depth: ignore any 16-char scratch dirs at repo root. The
# root cause (tests in packages/pi/src/loop.zig passing bare tmp.sub_path
# as workspace_root) was fixed by routing writes through
# .zig-cache/tmp/<sub_path>, but keep this glob in case another callsite
# regresses. No legit top-level dir in this repo is 16 chars long.
